sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor C as Client / Workload
    participant V as Vault OCI Plugin
    participant S as Vault Storage
    participant O as OCI Token Endpoint

    C->>V: `vault write oci/exchange` with caller JWT and `role`
    V->>S: Read backend config and requested plugin role
    S-->>V: `enforce_role_claim_match`, `role_claim_key`, role policy
    V->>V: Parse caller JWT payload only
    V->>V: Compare claim value to requested `role`

    alt Claim matches role
        V->>O: POST OAuth token exchange
        O-->>V: OCI session token
        V-->>C: Success response
    else Claim missing or mismatched
        V-->>C: Error response before OCI call
    end

